00:23:53.839 --> 00:23:55.039
It feels like a dream.

00:23:55.920 --> 00:23:56.480
Not old, not old.

00:23:56.480 --> 00:23:58.119
My Yingzi will never be old.

00:23:58.119 --> 00:23:59.119
Oh, stop it.

00:24:00.880 --> 00:24:01.599
Little Cai.

00:24:02.279 --> 00:24:04.559
You must come back to our Evergreen Residence often.

00:24:04.799 --> 00:24:06.839
Come back often to see us all.

00:24:07.200 --> 00:24:08.240
Of course.

00:24:08.319 --> 00:24:09.400
That's my maiden home.

00:24:09.640 --> 00:24:10.519
The day after tomorrow...

00:24:10.559 --> 00:24:12.359
I'll take Old Cao back for the homecoming.

00:24:12.480 --> 00:24:14.160
Good.

00:24:16.279 --> 00:24:16.940
Hurry, hurry!

00:24:18.299 --> 00:24:19.240
Auntie Cai, don't worry.

00:24:23.180 --> 00:24:23.740
What's wrong?

00:24:24.460 --> 00:24:25.500
What happened?

00:24:26.460 --> 00:24:28.180
Grandpa Cao had a sudden heart attack.

00:24:28.980 --> 00:24:30.059
How did that happen?

00:24:30.180 --> 00:24:31.339
On the wedding night...

00:24:31.339 --> 00:24:32.660
Maybe he got too excited.

00:24:33.019 --> 00:24:34.779
Exactly, his old heart couldn't take it.

00:24:34.779 --> 00:24:35.579
Yeah.

00:24:35.779 --> 00:24:36.940
Could it be that just now...

00:24:36.940 --> 00:24:38.660
It was the wine you toasted Elder Cao with?

00:24:38.980 --> 00:24:40.220
How can you say that, child?

00:24:40.500 --> 00:24:42.180
I was the one who got myself drunk just now.

00:24:42.259 --> 00:24:43.579
Old Cao didn't drink a drop.

00:24:43.700 --> 00:24:44.380
No...

00:24:44.500 --> 00:24:46.740
What if something bad happens to Elder Cao?

00:24:46.819 --> 00:24:48.819
Little Cai's house hasn't been transferred yet, right?

00:24:48.980 --> 00:24:49.940
That's right.